org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.view.layout.algorithm.standard
Class AbstractLayout<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.view.layout.algorithm.standard.AbstractLayout<T>
Type Parameters:
T -

Direct Known Subclasses:
KKLayout, SpringLayout
public abstract class AbstractLayout<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Layout<T>

AbstractLayout is an abstract class for implementations of Layout. It handles some of the basic functions: storing coordinates, maintaining the dimensions, initializing the locations, maintaining locked vertices.

Author:
Danyel Fisher, Scott White, Tom Nelson - converted to jung2, Sabina Sara Pfister - adaptation for Cytoscape
